[\fB\-\-helo\fR \fIhelo-identity\fR] [\fI\s-1OPTIONS\s0\fR]
.Sp
\&\fBspfquery\fR \fB\-\-pra\fR \fIpra-identity\fR \fB\-\-ip\-address\fR|\fB\-\-ip\fR \fIip-address\fR [\fI\s-1OPTIONS\s0\fR]
